CatDescriptText: The broadside reads: "Cabaret given by Modern Jazz Society of Pittsburgh, featuring Ahmad Jamal and his Trio, plus Walt Harper and his Orchestra, Sun., Nov. 9th, from 9:00 p.m. to 1:00 a.m., Kenny Litman's Copa, 818 Liberty Avenue, BYOB, Donation $2.50 per person."
TitMainTitle: Nine men posing around broadside advertising show with Ahmad Jamal and Walt Harper, in room with floral curtains and slipcovers
